{"type":"text","timestamp":1784385708850,"sessionID":"ses_08a55b97affezjS590Sxu4oUZ9","part":{"id":"prt_f75ad0ddb001fOlnBN0dWdu828","messageID":"msg_f75acf0c5001mHdLD20kOL41Ld","sessionID":"ses_08a55b97affezjS590Sxu4oUZ9","type":"text","text":"The detached prompt matches the canonical `fanout-run.cjs` lineage contract exactly. I am binding the override directly, skipping resolver and continuity-save writes, and will use the YAML-owned CLI executor path for one LEAF iteration at a time; the review target remains read-only.","time":{"start":1784385703387,"end":1784385708847},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_004103829d7737c6016a5b90a7608c81919df9a53c40fd97b2","phase":"commentary"}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1784385709065,"sessionID":"ses_08a55b97affezjS590Sxu4oUZ9","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_Oqly9dxgOpmH32yfeL9bH1om","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-deep-loop/deep-review/assets/deep_review_config.json"},"output":"<path>/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-deep-loop/deep-review/assets/deep_review_config.json</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: {\n2:   \"topic\": \"\",\n3:   \"sessionId\": \"\",\n4:   \"parentSessionId\": null,\n5:   \"lineageMode\": \"new\",\n6:   \"generation\": 1,\n7:   \"continuedFromRun\": null,\n8:   \"migrationWindowEndsAt\": \"\",\n9:   \"maxIterations\": 7,\n10:   \"convergenceThreshold\": 0.10,\n11:   \"antiConvergence\": {\n12:     \"minIterations\": 2,\n13:     \"convergenceMode\": \"default\",\n14:     \"stopPolicy\": \"fail-closed\"\n15:   },\n16:   \"stuckThreshold\": 2,\n17:   \"maxDurationMinutes\": 120,\n18:   \"maxToolCallsPerIteration\": 12,\n19:   \"maxMinutesPerIteration\": 10,\n20:   \"progressiveSynthesis\": false,\n21:   \"specFolder\": \"\",\n22:   \"createdAt\": \"\",\n23:   \"status\": \"initialized\",\n24:   \"releaseReadinessState\": \"in-progress\",\n25:   \"executionMode\": \"auto\",\n26:   \"executor\": {\n27:     \"kind\": \"native\",\n28:     \"model\": null,\n29:     \"reasoningEffort\": null,\n30:     \"serviceTier\": null,\n31:     \"sandboxMode\": null,\n32:     \"timeoutSeconds\": 900\n33:   },\n34:   \"mode\": \"review\",\n35:   \"reviewTarget\": \"\",\n36:   \"reviewTargetType\": \"spec-folder\",\n37:   \"reviewDimensions\": [\n38:     \"correctness\",\n39:     \"security\",\n40:     \"traceability\",\n41:     \"maintainability\"\n42:   ],\n43:   \"severityThreshold\": \"P2\",\n44:   \"crossReference\": {\n45:     \"core\": [\n46:       \"spec_code\",\n47:       \"checklist_evidence\"\n48:     ],\n49:     \"overlay\": [\n50:       \"skill_agent\",\n51:       \"agent_cross_runtime\",\n52:       \"feature_catalog_code\",\n53:       \"playbook_capability\"\n54:     ]\n55:   },\n56:   \"qualityGateThreshold\": true,\n57:   \"runtimeCapabilityResolver\": \".opencode/skills/system-deep-loop/deep-review/scripts/runtime-capabilities.cjs\",\n58:   \"reducerScriptPath\": \".opencode/skills/system-deep-loop/runtime/scripts/reduce-state.cjs\",\n59:   \"fileProtection\": {\n60:     \"deep-review-config.json\": \"immutable\",\n61:     \"deep-review-state.jsonl\": \"append-only\",\n62:     \"deep-review-findings-registry.json\": \"auto-generated\",\n63:     \"deep-review-strategy.md\": \"mutable\",\n64:     \"deep-review-dashboard.md\": \"auto-generated\",\n65:     \".deep-review-pause\": \"operator-controlled\",\n66:     \"review-report.md\": \"mutable\",\n67:     \"review-report-v*.md\": \"write-once\",\n68:     \"iteration-*.md\": \"write-once\"\n69:   },\n70:   \"reducer\": {\n71:     \"enabled\": true,\n72:     \"inputs\": [\n73:       \"latestJSONLDelta\",\n74:       \"newIterationFile\",\n75:       \"priorReducedState\"\n76:     ],\n77:     \"outputs\": [\n78:       \"findingsRegistry\",\n79:       \"dashboardMetrics\",\n80:       \"strategyUpdates\"\n81:     ],\n82:     \"metrics\": [\n83:       \"dimensionsCovered\",\n84:       \"findingsBySeverity\",\n85:       \"openFindings\",\n86:       \"resolvedFindings\",\n87:       \"convergenceScore\"\n88:     ]\n89:   },\n90:   \"_optimizerManaged\": {\n91:     \"description\": \"Fields managed by the offline loop optimizer (042.004). See optimizer-manifest.json for the canonical tunable/locked field registry.\",\n92:     \"manifestPath\": \".opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/scripts/optimizer/optimizer-manifest.json\",\n93:     \"tunableFields\": [\"convergenceThreshold\", \"stuckThreshold\", \"maxIterations\"],\n94:     \"lockedFields\": [\"lineageMode\", \"reducer\", \"fileProtection\", \"sessionId\", \"mode\", \"reviewDimensions\", \"antiConvergence.convergenceMode\", \"antiConvergence.stopPolicy\"],\n95:     \"promotionMode\": \"advisory-only\"\n96:   }\n97: }\n\n(End of file - total 97 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"{\n  \"topic\": \"\",\n  \"sessionId\": \"\",\n  \"parentSessionId\": null,\n  \"lineageMode\": \"new\",\n  \"generation\": 1,\n  \"continuedFromRun\": null,\n  \"migrationWindowEndsAt\": \"\",\n  \"maxIterations\": 7,\n  \"convergenceThreshold\": 0.10,\n  \"antiConvergence\": {\n    \"minIterations\": 2,\n    \"convergenceMode\": \"default\",\n    \"stopPolicy\": \"fail-closed\"\n  },\n  \"stuckThreshold\": 2,\n  \"maxDurationMinutes\": 120,\n  \"maxToolCallsPerIteration\": 12,\n  \"maxMinutesPerIteration\": 10,\n  \"progressiveSynthesis\": false,","truncated":false,"loaded":[],"display":{"type":"file","path":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-deep-loop/deep-review/assets/deep_review_config.json","text":"{\n  \"topic\": \"\",\n  \"sessionId\": \"\",\n  \"parentSessionId\": null,\n  \"lineageMode\": \"new\",\n  \"generation\": 1,\n  \"continuedFromRun\": null,\n  \"migrationWindowEndsAt\": \"\",\n  \"maxIterations\": 7,\n  \"convergenceThreshold\": 0.10,\n  \"antiConvergence\": {\n    \"minIterations\": 2,\n    \"convergenceMode\": \"default\",\n    \"stopPolicy\": \"fail-closed\"\n  },\n  \"stuckThreshold\": 2,\n  \"maxDurationMinutes\": 120,\n  \"maxToolCallsPerIteration\": 12,\n  \"maxMinutesPerIteration\": 10,\n  \"progressiveSynthesis\": false,\n  \"specFolder\": \"\",\n  \"createdAt\": \"\",\n  \"status\": \"initialized\",\n  \"releaseReadinessState\": \"in-progress\",\n  \"executionMode\": \"auto\",\n  \"executor\": {\n    \"kind\": \"native\",\n    \"model\": null,\n    \"reasoningEffort\": null,\n    \"serviceTier\": null,\n    \"sandboxMode\": null,\n    \"timeoutSeconds\": 900\n  },\n  \"mode\": \"review\",\n  \"reviewTarget\": \"\",\n  \"reviewTargetType\": \"spec-folder\",\n  \"reviewDimensions\": [\n    \"correctness\",\n    \"security\",\n    \"traceability\",\n    \"maintainability\"\n  ],\n  \"severityThreshold\": \"P2\",\n  \"crossReference\": {\n    \"core\": [\n      \"spec_code\",\n      \"checklist_evidence\"\n    ],\n    \"overlay\": [\n      \"skill_agent\",\n      \"agent_cross_runtime\",\n      \"feature_catalog_code\",\n      \"playbook_capability\"\n    ]\n  },\n  \"qualityGateThreshold\": true,\n  \"runtimeCapabilityResolver\": \".opencode/skills/system-deep-loop/deep-review/scripts/runtime-capabilities.cjs\",\n  \"reducerScriptPath\": \".opencode/skills/system-deep-loop/runtime/scripts/reduce-state.cjs\",\n  \"fileProtection\": {\n    \"deep-review-config.json\": \"immutable\",\n    \"deep-review-state.jsonl\": \"append-only\",\n    \"deep-review-findings-registry.json\": \"auto-generated\",\n    \"deep-review-strategy.md\": \"mutable\",\n    \"deep-review-dashboard.md\": \"auto-generated\",\n    \".deep-review-pause\": \"operator-controlled\",\n    \"review-report.md\": \"mutable\",\n    \"review-report-v*.md\": \"write-once\",\n    \"iteration-*.md\": \"write-once\"\n  },\n  \"reducer\": {\n    \"enabled\": true,\n    \"inputs\": [\n      \"latestJSONLDelta\",\n      \"newIterationFile\",\n      \"priorReducedState\"\n    ],\n    \"outputs\": [\n      \"findingsRegistry\",\n      \"dashboardMetrics\",\n      \"strategyUpdates\"\n    ],\n    \"metrics\": [\n      \"dimensionsCovered\",\n      \"findingsBySeverity\",\n      \"openFindings\",\n      \"resolvedFindings\",\n      \"convergenceScore\"\n    ]\n  },\n  \"_optimizerManaged\": {\n    \"description\": \"Fields managed by the offline loop optimizer (042.004). See optimizer-manifest.json for the canonical tunable/locked field registry.\",\n    \"manifestPath\": \".opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/scripts/optimizer/optimizer-manifest.json\",\n    \"tunableFields\": [\"convergenceThreshold\", \"stuckThreshold\", \"maxIterations\"],\n    \"lockedFields\": [\"lineageMode\", \"reducer\", \"fileProtection\", \"sessionId\", \"mode\", \"reviewDimensions\", \"antiConvergence.convergenceMode\", \"antiConvergence.stopPolicy\"],\n    \"promotionMode\": \"advisory-only\"\n  }\n}","lineStart":1,"lineEnd":97,"totalLines":97,"truncated":false}},"title":".opencode/skills/system-deep-loop/deep-review/assets/deep_review_config.json","time":{"start":1784385708992,"end":1784385709063}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_004103829d7737c6016a5b90accd1c819187033b5ceea553d5"}},"id":"prt_f75ad23ac001zRZKgsvqKg8jaN","sessionID":"ses_08a55b97affezjS590Sxu4oUZ9","messageID":"msg_f75acf0c5001mHdLD20kOL41Ld"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1784385709083,"sessionID":"ses_08a55b97affezjS590Sxu4oUZ9","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_VbukGcejAuw4OqPoORvUw1Wr","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-deep-loop/deep-review/assets/deep_review_strategy.md"},"output":"<path>/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-deep-loop/deep-review/assets/deep_review_strategy.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: ---\n2: title: Deep Review Strategy Template\n3: description: Runtime template copied to review/ during initialization to track review progress, dimension coverage, findings, and outcomes across iterations.\n4: trigger_phrases:\n5:   - \"deep review strategy template\"\n6:   - \"review dimension tracking\"\n7:   - \"exhausted review approaches\"\n8:   - \"review session tracking\"\n9: importance_tier: normal\n10: contextType: planning\n11: version: 1.11.0.13\n12: ---\n13: \n14: # Deep Review Strategy - Session Tracking Template\n15: \n16: Runtime template copied into the resolved `{artifact_dir}/` during initialization. Tracks review progress across iterations.\n17: \n18: ## 1. OVERVIEW\n19: \n20: ### Purpose\n21: \n22: Serves as the \"persistent brain\" for a deep review session. Records which dimensions remain, what was found (P0/P1/P2), what review approaches worked or failed, and where to focus next. Read by the orchestrator and agents at every iteration.\n23: \n24: ### Usage\n25: \n26: - **Init:** Orchestrator copies this template to `{artifact_dir}/deep-review-strategy.md` and populates Topic, Review Dimensions, Known Context, and Review Boundaries from config and memory context.\n27: - **Per iteration:** Agent reads Next Focus, reviews the assigned dimension/files, updates findings, marks dimensions complete, and sets new Next Focus.\n28: - **Mutability:** Mutable, updated by both orchestrator and agents throughout the session.\n29: - **Protection:** None (shared mutable state). Orchestrator validates consistency on resume.\n30: - **Ownership:** Machine-managed metrics and coverage blocks are wrapped in explicit ownership markers. Human commentary and operator overrides live outside those markers.\n31: \n32: ---\n33: \n34: ## 2. TOPIC\n35: [Review target description from config -- set during initialization]\n36: \n37: ---\n38: \n39: ## 3. REVIEW DIMENSIONS (remaining)\n40: <!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n41: - [ ] D1 Correctness, Logic errors, off-by-one, wrong return types, broken invariants\n42: - [ ] D2 Security, Injection, auth bypass, secrets exposure, unsafe deserialization\n43: - [ ] D3 Traceability, Spec/code alignment, checklist evidence, cross-reference integrity\n44: - [ ] D4 Maintainability, Patterns, clarity, documentation quality, safe follow-on change cost\n45: <!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n46: \n47: ---\n48: \n49: ## 4. NON-GOALS\n50: [What this review session is NOT trying to assess -- populated during initialization]\n51: \n52: ---\n53: \n54: ## 5. STOP CONDITIONS\n55: [Explicit conditions beyond convergence that should end the session -- populated during initialization]\n56: \n57: ---\n58: \n59: ## 6. COMPLETED DIMENSIONS\n60: <!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n61: [None yet -- populated as iterations complete dimension reviews]\n62: \n63: | Dimension | Verdict | Iteration | Summary |\n64: |-----------|---------|-----------|---------|\n65: | [D1 Correctness] | [PASS/CONDITIONAL/FAIL] | [N] | [1-sentence result] |\n66: <!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n67: \n68: ---\n69: \n70: ## 7. RUNNING FINDINGS\n71: <!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n72: - **P0 (Critical):** 0 active\n73: - **P1 (Major):** 0 active\n74: - **P2 (Minor):** 0 active\n75: - **Delta this iteration:** +0 P0, +0 P1, +0 P2\n76: \n77: [Findings are tracked in `deep-review-findings-registry.json`. This section provides a running count summary updated after each iteration.]\n78: <!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n79: \n80: ---\n81: \n82: ## 8. WHAT WORKED\n83: [First iteration -- populated after iteration 1 completes]\n84: - [Approach]: [Why it worked] (iteration N)\n85: \n86: ---\n87: \n88: ## 9. WHAT FAILED\n89: [First iteration -- populated after iteration 1 completes]\n90: - [Approach]: [Why it failed] (iteration N)\n91: \n92: ---\n93: \n94: ## 10. EXHAUSTED APPROACHES (do not retry)\n95: [Populated when a review approach has been tried from multiple angles without yielding new findings]\n96: \n97: ### [Category Name] -- BLOCKED (iteration N, N attempts)\n98: - What was tried: [specific review approaches attempted]\n99: - Why blocked: [root cause of exhaustion]\n100: - Do NOT retry: [explicit prohibition]\n101: \n102: ### [Category Name] -- PRODUCTIVE (iteration N)\n103: - What worked: [successful review approaches in this category]\n104: - Prefer for: [related dimensions where this category may help]\n105: \n106: ---\n107: \n108: ## 10A. SATURATED / SWEPT DIMENSIONS AND EXPANSION FRONTIER\n109: <!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n110: - Completed pivots: 0\n111: - Failed pivots: 0\n112: - Audited overrides: 0\n113: - Swept: none yet\n114: - Pivot lineage: none yet\n115: - Remaining frontier: none recorded\n116: <!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n117: \n118: ---\n119: \n120: ## 11. RULED OUT DIRECTIONS\n121: [Review angles that were investigated and definitively eliminated -- consolidated from iteration dead-end data]\n122: - [Approach]: [Why ruled out] (iteration N, evidence: [source])\n123: \n124: ---\n125: \n126: ## 12. NEXT FOCUS\n127: <!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n128: [Recommended focus area for the next iteration -- updated at end of each iteration. Includes target dimension and/or specific files to review.]\n129: <!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n130: \n131: ---\n132: \n133: ## 13. KNOWN CONTEXT\n134: [Populated during initialization from memory_context() results, if any prior work exists]\n135: \n136: ### Bounded Context Snapshot\n137: \n138: Populate during initialization before the first review dimension runs. Keep this pointer-based and scoped to the declared review target:\n139: \n140: - Target pointers: files, specs, symbols, or resource-map entries under review.\n141: - Behavior claims: acceptance criteria, public contracts, or docs to verify.\n142: - Reuse and conventions: existing patterns that define expected implementation shape.\n143: - Review risks and gaps: stale graph or memory caveats, missing files, and out-of-scope areas.\n144: \n145: Do not inline full source bodies. Do not dispatch the retired standalone context loop. Use this snapshot only to seed review dimensions and final traceability.\n146: \n147: ---\n148: \n149: ## 14. CROSS-REFERENCE STATUS\n150: <!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n151: [Alignment checks completed across core and overlay protocols]\n152: \n153: | Protocol | Level | Status | Iteration | Notes |\n154: |----------|-------|--------|-----------|-------|\n155: | `spec_code` | core | [pending/pass/partial/fail/blocked] | [N] | [details] |\n156: | `checklist_evidence` | core | [pending/pass/partial/fail/blocked] | [N] | [details] |\n157: | `skill_agent` | overlay | [pending/pass/partial/fail/blocked/notApplicable] | [N] | [details] |\n158: | `agent_cross_runtime` | overlay | [pending/pass/partial/fail/blocked/notApplicable] | [N] | [details] |\n159: | `feature_catalog_code` | overlay | [pending/pass/partial/fail/blocked/notApplicable] | [N] | [details] |\n160: | `playbook_capability` | overlay | [pending/pass/partial/fail/blocked/notApplicable] | [N] | [details] |\n161: <!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n162: \n163: ---\n164: \n165: ## 15. FILES UNDER REVIEW\n166: <!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n167: [Per-file coverage state table -- populated during initialization from scope discovery]\n168: \n169: | File | Dimensions Reviewed | Last Iteration | Findings | Status |\n170: |------|-------------------|----------------|----------|--------|\n171: | [path/to/file] | [D1, D3] | [N] | [0 P0, 1 P1, 2 P2] | [partial/complete] |\n172: <!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n173: \n174: ---\n175: \n176: ## 16. REVIEW BOUNDARIES\n177: <!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n178: - Max iterations: [from config]\n179: - Convergence threshold: [from config]\n180: - Rolling STOP threshold: 0.08\n181: - No-progress threshold: 0.05\n182: - Coverage stabilization passes required: 1\n183: - Session lineage: sessionId=[from config.sessionId], parentSessionId=[from config.parentSessionId], generation=[from config.generation], lineageMode=[from config.lineageMode]\n184: - Findings registry: `deep-review-findings-registry.json`\n185: - Release-readiness states: in-progress | converged | release-blocking\n186: - Per-iteration budget: [from config.maxToolCallsPerIteration] tool calls, [from config.maxMinutesPerIteration] minutes\n187: - Severity threshold: [from config.severityThreshold]\n188: - Review target type: [from config.reviewTargetType]\n189: - Cross-reference checks: core=[from config.crossReference.core], overlay=[from config.crossReference.overlay]\n190: - Started: [timestamp]\n191: <!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n192: \n193: ---\n194: \n195: ## 17. EXAMPLE (POPULATED)\n196: \n197: Reference snippet showing a partially populated strategy file mid-review. Use this as a visual anchor when opening a live strategy doc.\n198: \n199: ```markdown\n200: ## 1. REVIEW CHARTER\n201: - Target: .opencode/skills/system-deep-loop/deep-research (skill, v1.4.0)\n202: - Dimensions: correctness, test-coverage, cross-runtime-parity, observability\n203: - Stop conditions: rolling newInfoRatio < 0.08 for 2 iterations OR all dimensions converged OR max=7 reached\n204: - Success criteria: zero P0 in correctness; test-coverage P0 resolved or deferred with rationale\n205: \n206: ## 4. NEXT FOCUS\n207: - Dimension: test-coverage\n208: - Files: .opencode/skills/system-deep-loop/deep-research/scripts/reduce-state.cjs, .opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/scripts/tests/deep-research-contract-parity.vitest.ts\n209: - Why: Iteration 2 surfaced a P0 (convergence-path coverage gap); needs a focused follow-up before correctness can terminate PASS.\n210: \n211: ## 9. COVERAGE MATRIX\n212: | Dimension            | Status     | Iterations touched |\n213: |----------------------|------------|--------------------|\n214: | correctness          | converged  | 1                  |\n215: | test-coverage        | converging | 2, 4               |\n216: | cross-runtime-parity | converging | 3                  |\n217: | observability        | converging | 4                  |\n218: ```\n\n(End of file - total 218 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"---\ntitle: Deep Review Strategy Template\ndescription: Runtime template copied to review/ during initialization to track review progress, dimension coverage, findings, and outcomes across iterations.\ntrigger_phrases:\n  - \"deep review strategy template\"\n  - \"review dimension tracking\"\n  - \"exhausted review approaches\"\n  - \"review session tracking\"\nimportance_tier: normal\ncontextType: planning\nversion: 1.11.0.13\n---\n\n# Deep Review Strategy - Session Tracking Template\n\nRuntime template copied into the resolved `{artifact_dir}/` during initialization. Tracks review progress across iterations.\n\n## 1. OVERVIEW\n\n### Purpose","truncated":false,"loaded":[],"display":{"type":"file","path":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-deep-loop/deep-review/assets/deep_review_strategy.md","text":"---\ntitle: Deep Review Strategy Template\ndescription: Runtime template copied to review/ during initialization to track review progress, dimension coverage, findings, and outcomes across iterations.\ntrigger_phrases:\n  - \"deep review strategy template\"\n  - \"review dimension tracking\"\n  - \"exhausted review approaches\"\n  - \"review session tracking\"\nimportance_tier: normal\ncontextType: planning\nversion: 1.11.0.13\n---\n\n# Deep Review Strategy - Session Tracking Template\n\nRuntime template copied into the resolved `{artifact_dir}/` during initialization. Tracks review progress across iterations.\n\n## 1. OVERVIEW\n\n### Purpose\n\nServes as the \"persistent brain\" for a deep review session. Records which dimensions remain, what was found (P0/P1/P2), what review approaches worked or failed, and where to focus next. Read by the orchestrator and agents at every iteration.\n\n### Usage\n\n- **Init:** Orchestrator copies this template to `{artifact_dir}/deep-review-strategy.md` and populates Topic, Review Dimensions, Known Context, and Review Boundaries from config and memory context.\n- **Per iteration:** Agent reads Next Focus, reviews the assigned dimension/files, updates findings, marks dimensions complete, and sets new Next Focus.\n- **Mutability:** Mutable, updated by both orchestrator and agents throughout the session.\n- **Protection:** None (shared mutable state). Orchestrator validates consistency on resume.\n- **Ownership:** Machine-managed metrics and coverage blocks are wrapped in explicit ownership markers. Human commentary and operator overrides live outside those markers.\n\n---\n\n## 2. TOPIC\n[Review target description from config -- set during initialization]\n\n---\n\n## 3. REVIEW DIMENSIONS (remaining)\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n- [ ] D1 Correctness, Logic errors, off-by-one, wrong return types, broken invariants\n- [ ] D2 Security, Injection, auth bypass, secrets exposure, unsafe deserialization\n- [ ] D3 Traceability, Spec/code alignment, checklist evidence, cross-reference integrity\n- [ ] D4 Maintainability, Patterns, clarity, documentation quality, safe follow-on change cost\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n\n---\n\n## 4. NON-GOALS\n[What this review session is NOT trying to assess -- populated during initialization]\n\n---\n\n## 5. STOP CONDITIONS\n[Explicit conditions beyond convergence that should end the session -- populated during initialization]\n\n---\n\n## 6. COMPLETED DIMENSIONS\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n[None yet -- populated as iterations complete dimension reviews]\n\n| Dimension | Verdict | Iteration | Summary |\n|-----------|---------|-----------|---------|\n| [D1 Correctness] | [PASS/CONDITIONAL/FAIL] | [N] | [1-sentence result] |\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n\n---\n\n## 7. RUNNING FINDINGS\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n- **P0 (Critical):** 0 active\n- **P1 (Major):** 0 active\n- **P2 (Minor):** 0 active\n- **Delta this iteration:** +0 P0, +0 P1, +0 P2\n\n[Findings are tracked in `deep-review-findings-registry.json`. This section provides a running count summary updated after each iteration.]\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n\n---\n\n## 8. WHAT WORKED\n[First iteration -- populated after iteration 1 completes]\n- [Approach]: [Why it worked] (iteration N)\n\n---\n\n## 9. WHAT FAILED\n[First iteration -- populated after iteration 1 completes]\n- [Approach]: [Why it failed] (iteration N)\n\n---\n\n## 10. EXHAUSTED APPROACHES (do not retry)\n[Populated when a review approach has been tried from multiple angles without yielding new findings]\n\n### [Category Name] -- BLOCKED (iteration N, N attempts)\n- What was tried: [specific review approaches attempted]\n- Why blocked: [root cause of exhaustion]\n- Do NOT retry: [explicit prohibition]\n\n### [Category Name] -- PRODUCTIVE (iteration N)\n- What worked: [successful review approaches in this category]\n- Prefer for: [related dimensions where this category may help]\n\n---\n\n## 10A. SATURATED / SWEPT DIMENSIONS AND EXPANSION FRONTIER\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n- Completed pivots: 0\n- Failed pivots: 0\n- Audited overrides: 0\n- Swept: none yet\n- Pivot lineage: none yet\n- Remaining frontier: none recorded\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n\n---\n\n## 11. RULED OUT DIRECTIONS\n[Review angles that were investigated and definitively eliminated -- consolidated from iteration dead-end data]\n- [Approach]: [Why ruled out] (iteration N, evidence: [source])\n\n---\n\n## 12. NEXT FOCUS\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n[Recommended focus area for the next iteration -- updated at end of each iteration. Includes target dimension and/or specific files to review.]\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n\n---\n\n## 13. KNOWN CONTEXT\n[Populated during initialization from memory_context() results, if any prior work exists]\n\n### Bounded Context Snapshot\n\nPopulate during initialization before the first review dimension runs. Keep this pointer-based and scoped to the declared review target:\n\n- Target pointers: files, specs, symbols, or resource-map entries under review.\n- Behavior claims: acceptance criteria, public contracts, or docs to verify.\n- Reuse and conventions: existing patterns that define expected implementation shape.\n- Review risks and gaps: stale graph or memory caveats, missing files, and out-of-scope areas.\n\nDo not inline full source bodies. Do not dispatch the retired standalone context loop. Use this snapshot only to seed review dimensions and final traceability.\n\n---\n\n## 14. CROSS-REFERENCE STATUS\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n[Alignment checks completed across core and overlay protocols]\n\n| Protocol | Level | Status | Iteration | Notes |\n|----------|-------|--------|-----------|-------|\n| `spec_code` | core | [pending/pass/partial/fail/blocked] | [N] | [details] |\n| `checklist_evidence` | core | [pending/pass/partial/fail/blocked] | [N] | [details] |\n| `skill_agent` | overlay | [pending/pass/partial/fail/blocked/notApplicable] | [N] | [details] |\n| `agent_cross_runtime` | overlay | [pending/pass/partial/fail/blocked/notApplicable] | [N] | [details] |\n| `feature_catalog_code` | overlay | [pending/pass/partial/fail/blocked/notApplicable] | [N] | [details] |\n| `playbook_capability` | overlay | [pending/pass/partial/fail/blocked/notApplicable] | [N] | [details] |\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n\n---\n\n## 15. FILES UNDER REVIEW\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n[Per-file coverage state table -- populated during initialization from scope discovery]\n\n| File | Dimensions Reviewed | Last Iteration | Findings | Status |\n|------|-------------------|----------------|----------|--------|\n| [path/to/file] | [D1, D3] | [N] | [0 P0, 1 P1, 2 P2] | [partial/complete] |\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n\n---\n\n## 16. REVIEW BOUNDARIES\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n- Max iterations: [from config]\n- Convergence threshold: [from config]\n- Rolling STOP threshold: 0.08\n- No-progress threshold: 0.05\n- Coverage stabilization passes required: 1\n- Session lineage: sessionId=[from config.sessionId], parentSessionId=[from config.parentSessionId], generation=[from config.generation], lineageMode=[from config.lineageMode]\n- Findings registry: `deep-review-findings-registry.json`\n- Release-readiness states: in-progress | converged | release-blocking\n- Per-iteration budget: [from config.maxToolCallsPerIteration] tool calls, [from config.maxMinutesPerIteration] minutes\n- Severity threshold: [from config.severityThreshold]\n- Review target type: [from config.reviewTargetType]\n- Cross-reference checks: core=[from config.crossReference.core], overlay=[from config.crossReference.overlay]\n- Started: [timestamp]\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n\n---\n\n## 17. EXAMPLE (POPULATED)\n\nReference snippet showing a partially populated strategy file mid-review. Use this as a visual anchor when opening a live strategy doc.\n\n```markdown\n## 1. REVIEW CHARTER\n- Target: .opencode/skills/system-deep-loop/deep-research (skill, v1.4.0)\n- Dimensions: correctness, test-coverage, cross-runtime-parity, observability\n- Stop conditions: rolling newInfoRatio < 0.08 for 2 iterations OR all dimensions converged OR max=7 reached\n- Success criteria: zero P0 in correctness; test-coverage P0 resolved or deferred with rationale\n\n## 4. NEXT FOCUS\n- Dimension: test-coverage\n- Files: .opencode/skills/system-deep-loop/deep-research/scripts/reduce-state.cjs, .opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/scripts/tests/deep-research-contract-parity.vitest.ts\n- Why: Iteration 2 surfaced a P0 (convergence-path coverage gap); needs a focused follow-up before correctness can terminate PASS.\n\n## 9. COVERAGE MATRIX\n| Dimension            | Status     | Iterations touched |\n|----------------------|------------|--------------------|\n| correctness          | converged  | 1                  |\n| test-coverage        | converging | 2, 4               |\n| cross-runtime-parity | converging | 3                  |\n| observability        | converging | 4                  |\n```","lineStart":1,"lineEnd":218,"totalLines":218,"truncated":false}},"title":".opencode/skills/system-deep-loop/deep-review/assets/deep_review_strategy.md","time":{"start":1784385709001,"end":1784385709079}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_004103829d7737c6016a5b90accd248191a15fc3dfda6d25b6"}},"id":"prt_f75ad23c3001nyUrOowo8Oh2Ju","sessionID":"ses_08a55b97affezjS590Sxu4oUZ9","messageID":"msg_f75acf0c5001mHdLD20kOL41Ld"}}
