y.\n+\n+## 5. STOP CONDITIONS\n+- Legal convergence after all four dimensions and both core traceability protocols have coverage and stabilization.\n+- Hard ceiling of 10 iterations.\n+- Pause sentinel or unrecoverable state corruption.\n+\n+## 6. COMPLETED DIMENSIONS\n+<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n+None yet.\n+<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n+\n+## 7. RUNNING FINDINGS\n+<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n+- P0: 0 active\n+- P1: 0 active\n+- P2: 0 active\n+<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n+\n+## 8. WHAT WORKED\n+None yet.\n+\n+## 9. WHAT FAILED\n+- Spec Kit Memory context retrieval timed out twice before initialization; continue from direct repository evidence only.\n+\n+## 10. EXHAUSTED APPROACHES (do not retry)\n+- Memory-context retrieval for initialization is exhausted for this lineage after two timeouts.\n+\n+## 10A. SATURATED / SWEPT DIMENSIONS AND EXPANSION FRONTIER\n+<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n+- Completed pivots: 0\n+- Failed pivots: 0\n+- Audited overrides: 0\n+- Swept: none\n+- Pivot lineage: none\n+- Remaining frontier: correctness, security, traceability, maintainability\n+<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n+\n+## 11. RULED OUT DIRECTIONS\n+- Full style-corpus content audit: outside the declared packet-level review and not required to test the utilization contracts.\n+\n+## 12. NEXT FOCUS\n+<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n+Correctness inventory: reconcile parent/child lifecycle claims, planned-vs-implemented state, and metadata consistency before deeper dimensions.\n+<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n+\n+## 13. KNOWN CONTEXT\n+### Bounded Context Snapshot\n+- Target pointers: parent `spec.md`, `description.json`, `graph-metadata.json`; ten child packet specs and evidence docs; sk-design hub registry and six mode contracts.\n+- Behavior claims: research phases 001-003 are complete; phases 004-010 are planned; current runtime does not yet consume the extracted styles library.\n+- Reuse and conventions: lean phase-parent trio, child-owned implementation evidence, sk-design mode registry routing.\n+- Review risks and gaps: parent metadata may lag child state; planned child scaffolds may use completion-looking artifacts; memory context was unavailable; no root resource map exists.\n+- Out of scope: source-style extraction correctness and individual style bundle quality.\n+\n+## 14. CROSS-REFERENCE STATUS\n+<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n+| Protocol | Level | Status | Iteration | Notes |\n+|----------|-------|--------|-----------|-------|\n+| `spec_code` | core | pending | - | Compare packet claims to current sk-design contracts. |\n+| `checklist_evidence` | core | pending | - | Verify checked completion claims and phase status evidence. |\n+| `skill_agent` | overlay | notApplicable | - | Target is a spec folder. |\n+| `agent_cross_runtime` | overlay | notApplicable | - | Target is a spec folder. |\n+| `feature_catalog_code` | overlay | pending | - | Advisory where current feature claims exist. |\n+| `playbook_capability` | overlay | pending | - | Advisory where executable scenarios are claimed. |\n+<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n+\n+## 15. FILES UNDER REVIEW\n+<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n+| File group | Dimensions Reviewed | Last Iteration | Findings | Status |\n+|------------|---------------------|----------------|----------|--------|\n+| Parent lean trio | none | - | 0 | pending |\n+| Child packets 001-010 | none | - | 0 | pending |\n+| sk-design hub and mode contracts | none | - | 0 | pending |\n+<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n+\n+## 16. REVIEW BOUNDARIES\n+<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n+- Max iterations: 10\n+- Convergence threshold: 0.1\n+- Stop policy: convergence\n+- Rolling STOP threshold: 0.08\n+- No-progress threshold: 0.05\n+- Coverage stabilization passes required: 1\n+- Session lineage: sessionId=fanout-sol-a-1784385520599-ecg4bg, parentSessionId=null, generation=1, lineageMode=new\n+- Findings registry: `deep-review-findings-registry.json`\n+- Per-iteration budget: target 9, soft max 12, hard max 13 tool calls\n+- Severit