",\"claim\":\"The phase-004 contract permits a conforming implementation to hydrate a corpus path that resolves outside the styles root because no containment or symlink invariant is specified.\",\"evidenceRefs\":[\".opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/004-retrieval-substrate/spec.md:103-112\",\".opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/004-retrieval-substrate/spec.md:124-136\",\".opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/004-retrieval-substrate/spec.md:188-200\"],\"counterevidenceSought\":\"Searched phase-004/006/007/010 artifacts for realpath, canonicalization, traversal, root confinement, and symlink controls.\",\"alternativeExplanation\":\"Implementation may independently enforce containment, but neither containment nor fixed safe path generation is an acceptance criterion.\",\"finalSeverity\":\"P1\",\"confidence\":0.9,\"downgradeTrigger\":\"Downgrade to P2 if immutable manifest paths, canonical containment, symlink policy, and negative traversal fixtures become required.\"}},{\"id\":\"SOL-A-I002-P1-002\",\"severity\":\"P1\",\"category\":\"security\",\"dimension\":\"security\",\"status\":\"carried\",\"title\":\"The STUDY injection envelope records a boundary but does not neutralize untrusted instructions\",\"file\":\".opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/006-md-generator-study-exemplars/spec.md:104-117\",\"evidence\":\"The planned transformer injects corpus observations but specifies no data-only parsing, instruction rejection, or behavioral non-influence fixture.\",\"findingClass\":\"cross-consumer\",\"scopeProof\":\"Phase-006 artifacts repeat the envelope but lack prompt-injection behavior criteria; phase-007 authority ordering does not sanitize content.\",\"affectedSurfaceHints\":[\"study transformer\",\"STUDY prompt block\",\"adversarial fixtures\",\"runGuided retry\"],\"content_hash\":\"5d2be1beddf22032bde4e59d4bb0d4b73c7f3a54d1718ede78e6988f0c7918aa\",\"claimAdjudication\":{\"type\