-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/009-foundations-motion/spec.md:99-104\",\"evidence\":\"Phase 009 marks existing foundations and motion contracts as Create in spec and plan; phase 010's spec marks the existing transport directory Create while its plan says Add.\",\"findingClass\":\"matrix/evidence\",\"scopeProof\":\"Exact change-type searches covered phase-004-010 artifacts and direct reads proved all three runtime contracts already exist.\",\"affectedSurfaceHints\":[\"design-foundations contract\",\"design-motion contract\",\"Open Design transport\",\"phase implementation routing\"],\"content_hash\":\"b7cf0020db168dabf10e64564a8d5ffba7c8ef4299f5cd37ea364573d500cb45\",\"claimAdjudication\":{\"type\":\"claim-adjudication\",\"findingId\":\"SOL-A-I004-P1-001\",\"claim\":\"The phase-009 and phase-010 owning specs classify three existing runtime surfaces as creations, permitting implementation to replace or independently scaffold contracts that must instead be extended.\",\"evidenceRefs\":[\".opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/009-foundations-motion/spec.md:99-104\",\".opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/009-foundations-motion/plan.md:97-105\",\".opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/010-open-design-transport/spec.md:83-88\",\".opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/010-open-design-transport/plan.md:91-97\",\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-foundations/SKILL.md:1-15\",\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-motion/SKILL.md:1-15\",\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-mcp-open-design/SKILL.md:1-18\"],\"counterevidenceSought\":\"Reviewed affected-surface plans, implementation wording, current contracts, and phase-008 modification conventions for evidence that Create meant additive files only.\",\"alternativeExplanation\":\"Phase 009 later says additions and phase 010's plan says Add, reducing destructive intent; the owning action labels remain contradictory and phase 009 does not name t