"SOL-A-I004-P1-001\",\"classification\":\"carried_forward\",\"detail\":\"Additive prose contained replacement risk but did not reconcile owning Create/Add labels.\"}\n{\"type\":\"classification\",\"iteration\":5,\"findingId\":\"SUMMARY-P1-002\",\"classification\":\"resolved\",\"detail\":\"Reducer-generated cumulative-summary placeholder; not an authoritative finding.\"}\n{\"type\":\"classification\",\"iteration\":5,\"findingId\":\"SUMMARY-P1-003\",\"classification\":\"resolved\",\"detail\":\"Reducer-generated cumulative-summary placeholder; not an authoritative finding.\"}\n{\"type\":\"classification\",\"iteration\":5,\"findingId\":\"SUMMARY-P1-004\",\"classification\":\"resolved\",\"detail\":\"Reducer-generated cumulative-summary placeholder; not an authoritative finding.\"}\n{\"type\":\"traceability-check\",\"iteration\":5,\"protocolId\":\"claim_replay\",\"status\":\"partial\",\"findingRefs\":[\"SOL-A-I001-P1-001\",\"SOL-A-I002-P1-001\",\"SOL-A-I002-P1-002\",\"SOL-A-I003-P1-001\",\"SOL-A-I004-P1-001\"]}\n{\"type\":\"traceability-check\",\"iteration\":5,\"protocolId\":\"producer_consumer\",\"status\":\"partial\",\"findingRefs\":[\"SOL-A-I002-P1-001\"]}\n{\"type\":\"traceability-check\",\"iteration\":5,\"protocolId\":\"negative_test_gap\",\"status\":\"partial\",\"findingRefs\":[\"SOL-A-I002-P1-002\"]}\n{\"type\":\"traceability-check\",\"iteration\":5,\"protocolId\":\"metadata_consumer\",\"status\":\"fail\",\"findingRefs\":[\"SOL-A-I001-P1-001\",\"SOL-A-I003-P1-001\"]}\n{\"type\":\"traceability-check\",\"iteration\":5,\"protocolId\":\"change_classification\",\"status\":\"partial\",\"findingRefs\":[\"SOL-A-I004-P1-001\"]}\n{\"type\":\"graph-event\",\"iteration\":5,\"status\":\"unavailable\",\"graphCoverageMode\":\"graphless_fallback\",\"detail\":\"Detached-lineage prompt required graphless fallback; direct reads and exact searches supplied evidence.\"}\n{\"type\":\"ruled-out\",\"iteration\":5,\"candidate\":\"immediate child-resume misrouting\",\"reason\":\"Implementation-summary continuity precedes child spec fallback.\"}\n{\"type\":\"ruled-out\",\"iteration\":5,\"candidate\":\"generation and rights controls prove containment\",\"reason\":\"They do not test traversal, symlinks, or canonical-root escape.\"}\n{\"type\":\"ruled-out\",\"iteration\":5,\"candidate\":\"literal and span gates prove instruction neutrality\",\"reason\":\"Non-literal instruction influence can pass both signals.\"}\n{\"type\":\"ruled-out\",\"iteration\":5,\"candidate\":\"child-local blockers populate graph ordering\",\"reason\":\"Graph blocks are produced only from populated manual.depends_on entries.\"}\n{\"type\":\"ruled-out\",\"iteration\":5,\"candidate\":\"destructive replacement is the stated implementation intent\",\"reason\":\"ADRs and rollback plans consistently state additive work; only classification contradiction remains.\"}","lineStart":1,"lineEnd":20,"totalLines":20,"truncated":false}},"title":".opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/review/lineages/sol-a/deltas/iter-005.jsonl","time":{"start":1784389912110,"end":1784389912115}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_0f5140b5963ca347016a5ba1174f48819185f535b41c22704e"}},"id":"prt_f75ed45da001eNj7e6zWEwfEJs","sessionID":"ses_08a55b97affezjS590Sxu4oUZ9","messageID":"msg_f75ed1160001SgtmDLCQn9U23u"}}
