{"type":"text","timestamp":1784389973695,"sessionID":"ses_08a55b97affezjS590Sxu4oUZ9","part":{"id":"prt_f75ee32e4001cOUEBr2gTb14xV","messageID":"msg_f75edf6e6001TbfDQdG7Jri1ib","sessionID":"ses_08a55b97affezjS590Sxu4oUZ9","type":"text","text":"Mechanical verification passed for all five iterations: each has a narrative, exact verdict line, route proof, canonical state record, and delta. Convergence is now legal by the inline vote: rolling average does not vote STOP, MAD and stabilized full dimension coverage do, yielding `0.70`; all nine review gates pass or are rollout-inactive, with graphless fallback used because the strict lineage boundary forbids the external coverage-graph write.","time":{"start":1784389972708,"end":1784389973694},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0dd836f09b4cfbe4016a5ba1547c44819190e5b22e37d5b64c","phase":"commentary"}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1784389986505,"sessionID":"ses_08a55b97affezjS590Sxu4oUZ9","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"apply_patch","callID":"call_R9iOKkzVECixTTZv0ud7GyzI","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"patchText":"*** Begin Patch\n*** Update File: .opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/review/lineages/sol-a/deep-review-state.jsonl\n@@\n+{\"type\":\"event\",\"event\":\"claim_adjudication\",\"mode\":\"review\",\"run\":5,\"passed\":true,\"activeP0P1\":5,\"validatedPackets\":[\"SOL-A-I001-P1-001\",\"SOL-A-I002-P1-001\",\"SOL-A-I002-P1-002\",\"SOL-A-I003-P1-001\",\"SOL-A-I004-P1-001\"],\"missingPackets\":[],\"timestamp\":\"2026-07-18T15:44:00Z\",\"sessionId\":\"fanout-sol-a-1784385520599-ecg4bg\",\"generation\":1}\n+{\"type\":\"event\",\"event\":\"graph_convergence\",\"mode\":\"review\",\"run\":6,\"decision\":\"STOP_ALLOWED\",\"signals\":{\"adapter\":\"graphless_fallback\",\"dimensionCoverage\":1,\"coverageAge\":1,\"searchDebt\":0,\"mechanicalIterationsVerified\":5},\"blockers\":[],\"note\":\"The detached lineage boundary forbids the shared coverage-graph upsert; canonical direct-read/exact-search ledgers satisfy the graphless fallback gate without writing outside sol-a.\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-07-18T15:44:01Z\",\"sessionId\":\"fanout-sol-a-1784385520599-ecg4bg\",\"generation\":1}\n+{\"type\":\"event\",\"event\":\"stop_decision\",\"mode\":\"review\",\"run\":6,\"decision\":\"STOP\",\"stopReason\":\"converged\",\"weightedStopScore\":0.7,\"signals\":{\"rollingAverage\":{\"value\":0.1,\"threshold\":0.08,\"supportsStop\":false,\"weight\":0.3},\"madNoiseFloor\":{\"value\":0.494,\"latest\":0,\"supportsStop\":true,\"weight\":0.25},\"dimensionCoverage\":{\"value\":1,\"coverageAge\":1,\"supportsStop\":true,\"weight\":0.45}},\"gateResults\":{\"convergenceGate\":{\"pass\":true,\"score\":0.7},\"dimensionCoverageGate\":{\"pass\":true,\"covered\":[\"correctness\",\"security\",\"traceability\",\"maintainability\"],\"missing\":[]},\"p0ResolutionGate\":{\"pa