 P1 confirmed.\",\"linkedFindingId\":\"SOL-A-I003-P1-001\"},{\"id\":\"SL-005-05\",\"dimension\":\"maintainability\",\"targetRefs\":[\"phase-009\",\"phase-010\",\"current owners\"],\"bugClass\":\"change_classification\",\"hypothesis\":\"Create labels may unambiguously mean additive child files.\",\"searchActions\":[{\"method\":\"direct_read\",\"queryOrPath\":\"surface tables, ADRs, rollback, current contracts\",\"result\":\"Additive intent is clear, but owning Create/Add labels remain contradictory and file boundaries unnamed.\",\"evidenceRefs\":[\"009-foundations-motion/spec.md:99-104\",\"009-foundations-motion/decision-record.md:125-131\",\"010-open-design-transport/plan.md:91-97\"]}],\"disposition\":\"covered\",\"rationale\":\"Classification P1 retained with contained replacement risk.\",\"linkedFindingId\":\"SOL-A-I004-P1-001\"}],\"fixCompletenessReplay\":[{\"findingId\":\"SOL-A-I001-P1-001\",\"status\":\"carried_forward\",\"evidenceRefs\":[\"spec.md:13-25\",\"system-spec-kit/references/workflows/quick_reference.md:492-498\"],\"producerCoverage\":[\"continuity writers\"],\"consumerCoverage\":[\"parent pointer/list\",\"child resume\",\"canonical fallback\"],\"matrixCoverage\":[\"parent\",\"phase-002\",\"phase-003\"]},{\"findingId\":\"SOL-A-I002-P1-001\",\"status\":\"carried_forward\",\"evidenceRefs\":[\"004-retrieval-substrate/spec.md:103-136\",\"004-retrieval-substrate/checklist.md:86-102\"],\"producerCoverage\":[\"manifest paths\",\"hydrate CLI\"],\"consumerCoverage\":[\"source scan\",\"STUDY hydration\"],\"matrixCoverage\":[\"traversal\",\"symlink\",\"canonical-root escape\"]},{\"findingId\":\"SOL-A-I002-P1-002\",\"status\":\"carried_forward\",\"evidenceRefs\":[\"006-md-generator-study-exemplars/spec.md:104-117\",\"006-md-generator-study-exemplars/checklist.md:96-118\"],\"producerCoverage\":[\"transformer\",\"prompt block\"],\"consumerCoverage\":[\"buildWritePrompt\",\"buildPlan\",\"runGuided\"],\"matrixCoverage\":[\"literal\",\"span\",\"behavioral instruction influence\"]},{\"findingId\":\"SOL-A-I003-P1-001\",\"status\":\"carried_forward\",\"evidenceRefs\":[\"spec.md:121-126\",\"system-spec-kit/mcp_server/lib/graph/graph-metadata-parser.ts:1712-1723\"],\"producerCoverage\":[\"child dependency declarations\"],\"consumerCoverage\":[\"parent handoff\",\"causal graph blocks\"],\"matrixCoverage\":[\"phase-004-010 graph metadata\"]},{\"findingId\":\"SOL-A-I004-P1-001\",\"status\":\"carried_forward\",\"evidenceRefs\":[\"009-foundations-motion/spec.md:99-104\",\"010-open-design-transport/plan.md:91-97\"],\"producerCoverage\":[\"owning specs/plans\"],\"consumerCoverage\":[\"implementation dispatcher\",\"current mode/transport owners\"],\"matrixCoverage\":[\"foundations\",\"motion\",\"Open Design\"]}],\"newFindingsRatio\":0,\"findingStability\":1.0,\"noveltyJustification\":\"No new or refined finding emerged; focused skeptic/referee replay preserved five P1 severities and resolved only three reducer-generated placeholders.\",\"budgetProfile\":\"verify\",\"edgeCases\":[\"structural-impact analysis unavailable; graphless evidence used\",\"normal resume precedence contains but does not erase stale canonical continuity\",\"child-local blockers do not populate graph blocks\",\"additive prose contains replacement risk but not label contradiction\",\"no fixes applied: all active findings carried_forward\",\"content-hash merge warning preserved distinct SOL-A-I001-P1-001 and SOL-A-I003-P1-001 IDs\"],\"integrationEvidence\":[\"/speckit:resume continuity contracts\",\"system-spec-kit resume-ladder.ts\",\"system-spec-kit graph-metadata-parser.ts\",\"sk-design foundations/motion/Open Design contracts\"],\"ruledOut\":[\"immediate child-resume misrouting\",\"generation/rights tests as containment proof\",\"literal/span gates as injection proof\",\"child blockers as machine graph projection\",\"destructive replacement as stated intent\"],\"sessionId\":\"fanout-sol-a-1784385520599-ecg4bg\",\"parentSessionId\":null,\"generation\":1,\"lineageMode\":\"new\",\"continuedFromRun\":null,\"releaseReadinessState\":\"conditional\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-07-18T15:37:50Z\",\"durationMs\":480000}\n+{\"type\":\"event\",\"event\":\"claim_adjudication\",\"mode\":\"review\",\"run\":5,\"passed\":true,\"activeP0P1\":5,\"validatedPackets\":[\"SOL-A-I001-P1-001\",\"SOL-A-I002-P1-001\",\"SOL-A-I002-P1-002\",\"SOL-A-I003-P1-001\",\"SOL-A-I004-P1-001\"],\"missingPackets\":[],\"timestamp\":\"2026-07-18T15:44:00Z\",\"sessionId\":\"fanout-sol-a-1784385520599-ecg4bg\",\"generation\":1}\n+{\"type\":\"event\",\"event\":\"graph_convergence\",\"mode\":\"review\",\"run\":6,\"decision\":\"STOP_ALLOWED\",\"signals\":{\"adapter\":\"graphless_fallback\",\"dimensionCoverage\":1,\"coverageAge\":1,\"searchDebt\":0,\"mechanicalIterationsVerified\":5},\"blockers\":[],\"note\":\"The detached lineage boundary forbids the shared coverage-graph upsert; canonical direct-read/exact-search ledgers satisfy the graphless fallback gate without writing outside sol-a.\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-07-18T15:44:01Z\",\"sessionId\":\"fanout-sol-a-1784385520599-ecg4bg\",\"generation\":1}\n+{\"type\":\"event\",\"event\":\"stop_decision\",\"mode\":\"review\",\"run\":6,\"decision\":\"STOP\",\"stopReason\":\"converged\",\"weightedStopScore\":0.7,\"signals\":{\"rollingAverage\":{\"value\":0.1,\"threshold\":0.08,\"supportsStop\":false,\"weight\":0.3},\"madNoiseFloor\":{\"value\":0.494,\"latest\":0,\"supportsStop\":true,\"weight\":0.25},\"dimensionCoverage\":{\"value\":1,\"coverageAge\":1,\"supportsStop\":true,\"weight\":0.45}},\"gateResults\":{\"convergenceGate\":{\"pass\":true,\"score\":0.7},\"dimensionCoverageGate\":{\"pass\":true,\"covered\":[\"correctness\",\"security\",\"traceability\",\"maintainability\"],\"missing\":[]},\"p0ResolutionGate\":{\"pass\":true,\"activeP0\":0},\"evidenceDensityGate\":{\"pass\":true,\"avgEvidencePerFinding\":7.4},\"hotspotSaturationGate\":{\"pass\":true},\"claimAdjudicationGate\":{\"pass\":true,\"activeP0P1\":5},\"fixCompletenessReplayGate\":{\"